				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				at level 5 a new spell rank opens up to the druid... most all of the rank 5 spells are useful to the druid but i have found that learning grasping roots, camouflage,burst of fire, and gate is the best way to go at first...theres plenty of time to buy the other spells after you earn a bit more money..heading up to the butcherblok mountains is also a good choice hunting ground due to the spiders and snakes that are in abundance there..
